name: Haley Stranahan
coverLetter: I have no prior experience working directly with cannabis, but I am a quick, eager learner who's goal is to obtain as much knowledge possible to begin a career in this industry. The passion I have for cannabis goes beyond feeling physical affects; it is about how cannabis has evolved, the different components of it, and the various medicinal properties that enhance lives in so many ways. My schedule is very flexible and I would be available to start immediately.
